citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:45 AM on
05/17/2016. The inspector knocked at the front door of the residence and called the phone number provided. The
inspector also honked the vehicle horn and stayed on site for 30 minutes.
